l;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、专业技术职称、大学教师资格证申报相关政策。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">欢迎符合条件的教师及管理人员报名，有符合条件的院外社会人员也请积极举荐。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">报名截止日期：2012年3月2日</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">联系人：戴玫&nbsp;内线8517&nbsp; 邮箱</span><a href=\"mailto:daim@neusoft.com\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">daim@neusoft.com</span></a> \r\n</p>', '2013-11-17 23:58:54', '关于人力资源部面向全院、社会招聘薪酬福利主管等岗位的通知', null, '根据工作需要，学院人力资源部面向学院、社会招聘薪酬福利主管、人事主管、培训绩效主管。', '1');
INSERT INTO `t_article` VALUES ('40', 'admin', '8', '0', '<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">各位老师：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">根据工作需要，学院人力资源部面向学院、社会招聘薪酬福利主管、人事主管、培训绩效主管，具体要求如下：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">一、薪酬福利主管</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">招聘人数：1人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">工作职责：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1、负责人力成本测算； </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">2、负责人力成本的统计与分析；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3、负责执行和完善薪酬福利制度； </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、负责工资奖金的核定支持和制作发放；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">5、负责社保、公积金、企业年金及其它福利的管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">6、负责合同管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">7、负责E-HR信息化建设及维护。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">专业要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">人力资源管理、企业管理、或财务管理相关专业</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">学历要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">全日制本科及以上学历。 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">素质及要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1、熟练掌握excel操作技巧；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">2、强烈的合规性意识；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3、能准确进行信息沟通与传达；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、有学习和发展潜质。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">二、人事主管</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">招聘人数：1人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">工作职责：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1、负责人事管理制度建设： </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">2、负责劳动合同管理； </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3、负责办理人事手续；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、负责人事档案与信息管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">5、负责教工集体户口管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">6、负责考勤及请假管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">7、负责特别福利制作与发放；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">8、负责员工体检；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">9、日常行政事务管理</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">专业要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">企业管理或人力资源管理相关专业</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">学历要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">全日制本科及以上学历。 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">素质及要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1、熟练掌握excel操作技巧；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">2、强烈的合规性意识；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3、能准确进行信息沟通与传达；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、有学习和发展潜质。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">三、培训绩效主管</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">招聘人数：1人</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">工作职责：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1、负责员工发展规划： </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">2、负责员工发展体系建设：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3、负责员工绩效管理体系建设； </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、负责员工培养与发展、员工绩效管理制度建设；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">5、负责骨干员工培养；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">6、负责培训审批与管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">7、负责培训执行与实施；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">8、负责员工绩效考核；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">9、负责部门绩效管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">10、中层、基层干部绩效管理</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">11、评优工作；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">12、试用期员工转正考核；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">13、劳动争议管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">14、在职攻读学位管理；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">15、在双师素质教师资格管理。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">专业要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">企业管理或人力资源管理相关专业</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">学历要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">硕士及以上学历，人力资源培训岗位经验2年以上或人力资源管理经验5年以上。 </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">专业知识要求：</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">1、人力资源管理、组织行为学和管理学知识；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">2、行业知识；</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">3、组织变革、职位分析预评估、任职资格管理知识</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">4、专业技术职称、大学教师资格证申报相关政策。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">欢迎符合条件的教师及管理人员报名，有符合条件的院外社会人员也请积极举荐。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">报名截止日期：2012年3月2日</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-bottom:0px;line-height:21px;widows:2;text-transform:none;list-style-type:none;font-variant:normal;text-indent:2em;margin:0px;padding-left:0px;padding-right:0px;font-family:;white-space:normal;orphans:2;letter-spacing:normal;word-spacing:0px;padding-top:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;\">联系人：戴玫&nbsp;内线8517&nbsp; 邮箱</span><a href=\"mailto:daim@neusoft.com\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">daim@neusoft.com</span></a> \r\n</p>', '2013-11-17 21:51:26', '关于人力资源部面向全院、社会招聘薪酬福利主管等岗位的通知', 'uploadFile/article/upload/2013/10/091143a6-3eb6-4153-8682-fcfbb8800e87.jpg', '根据工作需要，学院人力资源部面向学院、社会招聘薪酬福利主管、人事主管、培训绩效主管.', '1');
